@startuml
actor User
participant Browser
participant "Vaadin Client Engine" as VCE
participant "Spring Boot Application" as SBA
participant "Vaadin Flow Server" as VFS
participant "Service Layer" as SL
participant "Database"

User -> Browser : HTTP GET /
Browser -> VCE : Load Bootstrap + UI JSON
VCE -> VFS : Establish connection

== Navigation / Event Flow ==
User -> Browser : Click Button
Browser -> VCE : Event triggered
VCE -> VFS : Send event as JSON
VFS -> SBA : Map to Java Component
VFS -> SL : Execute Business Logic
SL -> Database : Query/Update
Database --> SL : Response
SL --> VFS : Return data/state
VFS -> VCE : Return UI Patch JSON
VCE -> Browser : DOM Update

== Optional Server Push ==
SBA -> VFS : Push update
VFS -> VCE : Send async patch
VCE -> Browser : Apply changes
@enduml
